{"tid":166650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尋物 求連登仔幫手","createTime":"2017-03-22T09:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T09:40:12.000Z","uid":69987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16ebfc7d2b28b7e48ae8cb29abead3713dd9288c","tid":166650,"uid":69987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"雖然我知我搵既野會比人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係對我黎講真係好有意義<br />\n我好想搵番佢出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25onD98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25onD98.jpg&h=1edfbd21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我幾年前係miniso買既<br />\n原本諗住結婚果時係新居用<br />\n點知婚又結唔成 女朋友都走埋<br />\n但係我真係好想搵番呢對牙刷架<br />\n因為我比左隻豬仔佢 但佢唔見左<br />\n有無連登仔屋企有買未用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以賣比我/送比我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}